ype? What are the statistical characteristics of each syndrome type in terms\nof occurrence of symptoms? How can we determine the syndrome type(s) of a\npatient?\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Oct 2014 07:32:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Jan 2015 04:13:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 15 Jun 2015 10:58:52 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2016 08:29:49 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 24 Feb 2016 16:05:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-25"}
