ood\nunderstanding of both the physics and the chemistry behind the system and\npoints to a general route for designing new families of self-propelled\nparticles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Oct 2014 15:39:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-28"}
